name: Rimmel London Lasting Finish Lipstick by Kate Nude 42 Apricot Nude
review: Tolle Farbabgabe. Cremig und angenehm zu tragen. Sehr gut beim Auftragen. Haltbarkeit wie jeder normale Lippenstift. Lipliner ab Ü40 ist notwendig. Angenehmer Geruch. Mein absoluter Liebling unter meinen vielen Lippenstiften. Jederzeit zu empfehlen. Vor allen auch bei jungen Mädels. Keine Farbe die aufdringlich wirkt. 5 von 5 Krönchen.

name: Rimmel London Lasting Finish Lipstick by Kate Nude 42 Apricot Nude
review: Me gustaria saber si su fabricacion es reciente o son stock de hace bastantes años puesto que los retiraron del mercado al menos en España. Pero es mi pintalabios favorito, no es fijo pero hidrata y luego se seca un poco. Color 48 dark nude

name: Rimmel London Lasting Finish Lipstick by Kate Nude 42 Apricot Nude
review: I bought this on a whim- considering the 100+ lipsticks I own, it wasn't exactly a "necessity" lol- but now it is!! It's so rich & creamy- even if my lips aren't 100% smooth it seems to blur any imperfections, and it doesn't make my lips feel dry at all.As a brunette with olive tone skin, it can be hard to find a nude shade that doesn't completeley "wash out" my lips, but this shade is very flattering, especially when paired with a bold eye and no other makeup! I also love that I could put it on without a mirror if need be (not something you can do with red shades!)It isn't exactly long-lasting as the title suggests, I had to re-apply about 3 times in the day, but I didn't mind because the packaging is so cute, I love it!!
date: Reviewed in the United States on 29 December 2023
